---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Overseas Business Development | MarketOps" description="Expand beyond borders and grow without limits. Strategic international market entry, global lead generation, cross-border partnerships, and export planning.">
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-wrapper">
    <div class="hero-overlay" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.4) 0%, var(--bg-main) 100%);"></div>
    <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center;">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll">
        <div class="badge-lead">Global Business Expansion</div>
        <h1 class="gradient-text" style="font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4.2rem); max-width: 950px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;">
          Expand Beyond Borders. <br><span class="gradient-text-alt" style="font-weight: 800;">Grow Without Limits.</span>
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;">
          We help businesses unlock international opportunities and connect with global audiences through strategic overseas business development solutions.
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="#calendly" class="btn btn-primary">Book Strategy Call</a>
          <a href="#what-we-do" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Solutions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DO SECTION -->
  <section id="what-we-do" class="section-padding" style="background: #0d121f;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">Our Capabilities</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We Build Strong Global Growth Systems for Your Brand</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto;">Our end-to-end support enables brands to transition safely from local players to globally recognized operators.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📊</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">International Market Research &amp; Entry</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Thorough analysis of target demographics, localized search trends, pricing, competitor mapping, and compliance guidelines to form a bulletproof entry roadmap.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📞</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Global Lead Gen &amp; Outreach</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Constructing scalable B2B outbound campaign pipelines, custom visual pitch portfolios, and direct outreach mechanisms to secure premium global client responses.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🤝</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Cross-Border Partnerships</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Connecting your brand with overseas distributors, regional sales agencies, local logistics managers, and international affiliate channels.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">✈️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Export &amp; Expansion Planning</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Formulating cross-border trade steps, localized pricing structures, shipping fulfillment setups, and promotional cycles to scale volumes efficiently.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">👑</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Digital Global Branding</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Re-aligning your visual layouts, value communication assets, brand voice, and digital positioning to match global standards and inspire buying trust instantly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll">
          <div style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📈</div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Centralized Growth Dashboard</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Constant monitoring of cross-border ad performance, global lead pipelines, regional sales cycles, and localized campaign ROI indicators.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY CHOOSE US SECTION -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--bg-main);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">Why MarketOps</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Why Choose MarketOps for Global Expansion</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">We go beyond standard marketing, acting as your dedicated cross-border growth partners.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;">
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 2rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🌍</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Global Market Intel</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5;">
            Strong, localized understanding of buying psychology and ad behavior in major international hubs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 2rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">📈</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Data-Driven</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5;">
            Every market entry plan is backed by demand volumes and hard competitor spend metrics.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 2rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🛠️</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">End-to-End Setup</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5;">
            We handle everything from global ad channels setup to international lead outreach sequences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-panel reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: 2rem; text-align: center;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">💎</div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Measurable Growth</h4>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5;">
            Absolute focus on tangible client sales metrics, international ROAS thresholds, and recurring values.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRANSITION CALLOUT SECTION -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: #080c14; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="badge-lead">Grow Globally with Confidence</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Take your brand from local recognition to global presence</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
          Implement a clear, structured, and highly scalable international expansion strategy designed for long-term profit.
        </p>
        <a href="#calendly" class="btn btn-primary">Book Your Free Expansion Strategy Session</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQS SECTION -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--bg-main);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <div class="badge-lead">FAQ</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Everything you need to know about our Overseas Business Development & Global Entry solutions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-wrapper reveal-on-scroll">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">1. What is Overseas Business Development and how does it help my brand?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>It represents strategic solutions to expand your business presence, lead generation pipelines, and brand sales into international markets (such as US, Europe, Middle East, and Southeast Asia) using localized intelligence and global branding.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">2. Which global markets do you specialize in for expansion?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We specialize in expanding brands into North America (US & Canada), the United Kingdom, Europe, the UAE & Middle East, and cross-border APAC regions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">3. How do you conduct international market research?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We analyze consumer demand trends, search behavior volumes, competitor density maps, localized pricing sensitivities, and local regulatory requirements before proposing an entry strategy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">4. What is your global lead generation process?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We use hyper-targeted B2B outreach campaigns, localized digital positioning, global search engine indexing, and international paid acquisition funnels to connect you directly with qualified corporate decision-makers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 5 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">5. How do you handle cross-border partnerships?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We assist in identifying, reaching out to, and structuring partnership proposals with overseas distributors, agencies, retail channels, and affiliate networks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 6 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">6. Do you support export planning and compliance setups?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We provide the digital and marketing infrastructure roadmap for exports, aligning international digital branding, pricing, and messaging with global trade guidelines.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 7 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">7. How does digital branding differ globally vs locally?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Global branding requires careful adaptation to local cultural nuances, distinct messaging focus (e.g., highlighting global shipping speeds or US-compliance standards), and localized imagery.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 8 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">8. What is the typical timeline for an overseas expansion campaign?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>Initial research and strategy take 3-4 weeks. Launching active international outreach pipelines and global marketing campaigns typically yields qualified leads and brand traction within 60 to 90 days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 9 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">9. How do we track the performance of international expansion?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We track key global metrics including international lead acquisition cost (CPL), market penetration ratios, global search impressions, and multi-currency return on ad spend (ROAS).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 10 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-title">10. Why should we partner with MarketOps for global expansion?</span>
            <svg class="accordion-icon w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>We combine deep global market understanding, data-driven cross-border growth strategies, premium digital positioning, and end-to-end B2B outreach execution to secure a sustainable international footprint for your brand.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CALENDLY EMBED SECTION -->
  <section id="calendly" class="section-padding" style="background: #080c14;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal-on-scroll" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Setup Your Free Global Strategy Consultation</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Connect with a global expansion strategist today to review target markets and export structures.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="calendly-section reveal-on-scroll">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What We Will Discover:</h3>
            <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">[01]</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">Market Demand Review</h4>
                  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">Evaluation of buyer search densities and direct competitor footprints inside your targets.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">[02]</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">B2B Lead Channels Map</h4>
                  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">Identify which digital outbound directories and intent patterns match your B2B specs.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan); font-weight: bold;">[03]</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;">Scale Horizon Plan</h4>
                  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">A multi-stage roadmap specifying lead targets, brand adjustments, and budget brackets.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem; text-align: center;">
            <h4 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--font-heading);">Schedule Session</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Select slot on our live team calendar</p>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
              <a href="https://wa.me/919424995426" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">💬 WhatsApp Direct booking</a>
              <a href="mailto:connect@marketops.in" class="btn btn-secondary" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">📧 Email: connect@marketops.in</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
